Mohammed VI of Morocco
siwkay niza tatama a tademaw, nalecuhan i 8 a bulad 21 a demiad, Mohammed VI of Morocco, u misingkiway. 1963 a mihcaan nalecuhan) u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Morocco ayza sa ci Mohammed VI of Morocco, micakat a demiad sa i 1999 a mihca 6 bulad 23 demiad.
